$ Oracle: Init parameter AWR_PDB_AUTOFLUSH_ENABLED
@ awr_pdb_autoflush_enabled

The value of `awr_pdb_autoflush_enabled` controls whether automatic → development/databases/Oracle/Automatic-Workload-Repository#ora-awr-snapshot[AWR snapshots] for indivdual PDBs are enabled or disabled.
-
By default, automatic snapshots are enabled for a CDB but disabled for PDBs.
-
In order to set automatic snapthos for a PDB, the value of `awr_pdb_autoflush_enabled` must be set to `true` when connected to the PDB.

sa:

  → development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/init-parameters
